9. What are the different types of nail rhinestones available in the market?
Common types of nail rhinestones include flatback, pointed back, and hotfix rhinestones.

10. What are the key application areas for nail rhinestones?
Nail rhinestones are primarily used in nail art salons, spas, and by individual consumers for personal grooming.

